
How to use this Repository
===========================

git checkout -b user/pmallick/hack-01

python -m venv myenv

source myenv/bin/activate

pip freeze (Nothing should installed)

pip install -r requirements.txt

pip freeze (you should get everything from requirements.txt installed)

Run python app.py at the terminal under myenv development environment

You should get something as follows

python app.py
 * Serving Flask app 'app'
 * Debug mode: on
WARNING: This is a development server. Do not use it in a production deployment. Use a production WSGI server instead.
 * Running on all addresses (0.0.0.0)
 * Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000
 * Running on http://<your machine IP>:5000
Press CTRL+C to quit
 * Restarting with stat
 * Debugger is active!

On your web browser use the link http://<your machine IP>:5000 or http://127.0.0.1:5000
